citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 0945 on
29-JAN-19.
The inspector arrived at 9:45am but the facility owner was not on the premises. Via phone call, the owner stated
that she was currently at work and she was unable to facilitate inspection.
